ygData.subject: Re: twinked?
ygData.msgSnippet: I m thinking back in old school, when I first started playing. The FBR back then was the GOD robe....when the oracle robe was found, people nearly fell over
ygData.messageBody:
I'm thinking back in old school, when I first started playing. The FBR back
then was the GOD robe....when the oracle robe was found, people nearly fell
over themselves just to do an inspect on me <G>

Lana

Enchanters can make tons of cash just running around casting clarity for 10
plat a pop which is the going rate most of the time.. considering the SoW
costs about 300-400 plat, that's an easy buy after an hour or two of
buffing. Silversilk leggings 100 plat, that's like 20 minutes if that.
Oracle robe is maybe a 1000, but that's not too hard to have accumulated by
level 30.
